        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The procedure does not account for potential SQL injection risks, although the use of parameters mitigates this to some extent. However, ensuring that input is sanitized and validated is always a good practice."
